data.description: Come live and play the country club life style in Indian Palms Country Club.Enjoy this single story open floor plan.  Spacious Kitchen with Granite Large Island. New Updated Stove Hood, New Dishwasher and new Kitchen Faucet  A .C. Condenser replaced with new one,  New furnace, new garage opener, newly painted garage door.Tile floors through out the home, Ceiling Fans, Crown Moldings, Beautiful Valences  Window Treatments. Bedrooms and Bathrooms in Immaculate conditions, home is just welcoming you to move in.Back yard with large Patio Slab and grassy area with well maintain mature plant life. There is a space for your home garden.HOA Takes care of the front yard. Country Club Amenities :  golf course, five pools, gym, tennis, picket ball courts, bocce ball, five updated bathrooms and toilets  and 24 hour gated security.The community has hotel, restaurant  and banquet rooms.Investors this home rents well,  is close to the famous Coachella and Stage Coach Music festival and the Polo Grounds. Enjoy Date and Tamale Festivals. Minutes away from Ranch Polo Equestrian Center. Hiking ,bike trails, and horseback riding close by.   International and private airports are close .
